{"tid":1593283,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"未成年市民8.31太子站內遭警毆傷　父代子入稟告一哥","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:20:03.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8967f74eb11b1ea6406abadb429c2cdd8de45a56","tid":1593283,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190925/large/1569383167_fa2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190925%2Flarge%2F1569383167_fa2f.jpg&h=ba448331&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31有市民自發到港島各區「行街」，其後演變成嚴重警民衝突。大批防暴警察及速龍小隊衝進港鐵太子站內車廂，以警棍無差別的毆打市民，造成多人受傷。一名當天在站內的未成年市民，由父親代表入稟區域法院，指稱當日遭警方毆打致受傷，控告警務處處長並提出索償。<br />\n<br />\n李姓原告由父親代表入稟，被告警務處處長由律政司代表。入稟狀指，原告今年8月31日於港鐵太子站內遭受被告、其僱員及或其代理人毆打及或疏忽對待，因而受傷，原告為此向被告申索，包括一般、特定賠償，以及法庭認為適合的加重及懲罰性賠償。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀未述明原告的詳細傷勢，亦未透露索償額，而區域法院最高申索額為300萬元。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：DCPI3161/19】"},{"pid":"5627b25b89591b8c269cfd36bfbb5c4c16b6dd29","tid":1593283,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:07:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190925/60082151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60082151&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9Ic%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=31856ac4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190925%2F60082151&h=abfcb630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190925/60082151</a>"},{"pid":"8ea36e60a39eef16973e7f4909a1e55b1463366e","tid":1593283,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"7256f026543a8b5a7631b360b91135dd3faeef60","tid":1593283,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"果位手足要小心人身安全<br />\n依家周街都係拎住警棍既休班塔利班"},{"pid":"e79a4f57d6488c6defdca1436546c791cc5d61bf","tid":1593283,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8405947ef2afec40a69164f636f60df13aa351c","tid":1593283,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3078684410d3bfe2cc42a5de80d69f47aaaed563","tid":1593283,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:20:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"}]}